---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <main>
    <section id="hero" class="section">
      <div class="overlay"></div>
      <div class="container">
        <h1>SHOOT YOUR SHOT with OJUBABES!</h1>
        <p>Ready to find your perfect match? Fill out our detailed profile questionnaire to join the exclusive OJUBABES community.</p>
        <a href="/register" class="button">START REGISTRATION</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="welcome-video" class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="video-container">
          <iframe 
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/55FHnJS3OWA?autoplay=1&mute=1&loop=1&playlist=55FHnJS3OWA"
            title="YouTube video player" 
            frameborder="0" 
            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" 
            allowfullscreen></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="testimonials" class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Don't Believe Us? See Who Found Love!</h2>
        <div class="testimonial-container">
          <div class="testimonial">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542103749-8ef59b94f475?q=80&w=2670&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="Couple 1">
            <p>"We are so grateful to OJUBABES for bringing us together. We couldn't be happier!"</p>
            <h4>- Funke & Tunde</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1524250502761-5ac945e200f4?q=80&w=2564&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="Couple 2">
            <p>"The detailed profiles made all the difference. We knew we were a good match before we even met."</p>
            <h4>- Aisha & Emeka</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1567967455559-4e0e04bd1b1d?q=80&w=2574&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="Couple 3">
            <p>"I was skeptical about online matchmaking, but OJUBABES proved me wrong. I found the love of my life!"</p>
            <h4>- Chioma & David</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1530092285049-1c42085fd395?q=80&w=2574&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="Couple 4">
            <p>"The process was so easy and personalized. We felt understood from the very beginning."</p>
            <h4>- Sade & Femi</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1604928141068-a0d4f2b5d65b?q=80&w=2574&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="Couple 5">
            <p>"A fantastic service for anyone serious about finding a partner. Highly recommended!"</p>
            <h4>- Ife & Yemi</h4>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <style>
    #hero {
      position: relative;
      background-image: url('/download.jpeg');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 100px 20px;
    }

    .overlay {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
      z-index: 1;
    }

    #hero .container {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .social-icons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 15px;
    }

    .social-icon img {
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      transition: transform 0.3s;
    }

    .social-icon img:hover {
      transform: scale(1.2);
    }

    #welcome-video .video-container {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      border-radius: 15px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      padding-top: 56.25%; /* 16:9 Aspect Ratio */
    }

    #welcome-video iframe {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      border: none;
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
